reviewText: I'm in season 2 and the only thing is that 3 episodes were for closed caption. Other than that they are terrific. Love watching them with no interruptions.
Very happy with NCIS
NCIS is a fantastic series. Action, characters, plots all well developed and interesting. Also, the vender was fantastic; got my shipment in just a few days. Very satisfied with service and product.
I have always been an asiduous fan since it started. I just love all the episodes, characters, plot, etc.

Everything was just as described, shipped very quickly and was a great price!!
Totally satisfied and excited to start watching my new DVDs.

Thank you giftsandpresents!!

I would not recommend purchasing this set.  Granted, we are just into season 3 of 11, but only 4-5 of the 40 or so episodes have been high def.  Picture quality on the non-HD shows has been ok at best.  One entire disc, 4 episodes, had subtitles the entire episodes that had no option to turn them off.  Quite annoying.
NCIS is just awesome
I honestly could not have been more satisfied with this purchase.
DVDs are in great shape and I love being able to watch my favorite episodes whenever I want!!!!
we love the ncis cd they are great and would say to anyone to buy it
Best show on TV. Supper!!
Great series still
So far all the disks seem to be working just fine - I really like the series and I am glad to catch up on the earlier years that I had missed.

This was a great deal. All of the dvd cases were new and still in plastic. Some of the episodes in season 1 won't play, but since it appears to be brand new I'm going to say it's not the sellers fault. Would buy from this seller again.
Love them even though one case had the same episode from a season
the best show on television. glad I bought the series
Season six has major problems. Could not watch

Having only recently discovered this gem of a television show, I was excited to get ALL of the earlier episodes so I can watch commercial free. So far, there has been NO issues with the individual DVDs (only up to season 4 at the moment), except for the darn trailers on disc one of season 2; had to run them as you cannot speed through from the controls.
Movies are great plastic containers are good better than some other plastic containers I bought that came broken with the movies sliding around. Happy with these ones.
I looked everywhere to find this, finally found it at a great price on Amazon. Love it. And grateful I found it.
Awesome!
Very well pleased.
They are great and without commercials, I am enjoying them to the fullest.
Love NCIS and these DVD were in great condition and play well.
